{"id":111248,"type":2,"name":"Mater's Tall Tales Season 2","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/94/fe/111248_9tZ79.jpg","rating":{"total":5,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":1,"5":0,"6":2,"7":1,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5.2},"summary":"　　新的一季中，拖线（Larry the Cable Guy 配音）好玩有趣而想象力十足的幻想故事仍在继续。在新的冒险中，他曾经和一架也叫拖线的UFO宝宝玩耍，学会了飞翔的本领；也曾远赴重洋，以进口车的身份在东京参加甩尾王大比拼；还以“拖线喀”的绰号混迹摔角界，挑战一辆辆强壮的大脚卡车；还当过重金属歌手、宇航员、私人侦探，真可谓经历丰富。当然他的好哥们闪电麦昆（Keith Ferguson 配音）还是不相信拖线的信口开河，可是每一次又不由自主地成为拖线故事中的重要角色。真真假假，分辨不清。在私人侦探中，短片还揭示了拖线缺少一盏车头灯的因由。 \r\n 　　拖线狂想曲》为皮克斯继《赛车总动员》后，以配角拖线为主角制作的系列动画短片，供迪斯尼电视频道播放。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>拖线狂想曲第二季</li><li><span>话数: </span>6</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>2009年11月20日</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/22013\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">John Lasseter</a></li><li><span>脚本: </span><a href=\"/person/22013\">John Lasseter</a></li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/7960\">Pixar Animation Studios</a></li>","collection":{"wish":3,"collect":12,"dropped":3},"tags":[{"name":"pixar","count":4},{"name":"欧美","count":3},{"name":"TV","count":3},{"name":"短片","count":2},{"name":"美国","count":1},{"name":"3D","count":1},{"name":"2009","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":424260,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/424260","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":424261,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/424261","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":424262,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/424262","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":424263,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/424263","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":424264,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/424264","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":424265,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/424265","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","durat